info.name: natphoto.me API Documentation
info.description:
# Introduction
Pulls data from the database at natphoto.me

# Overview
All of the data stored in this database are pulled from credible sources such as nps.gov (National Park Information), flickr.com (Photograph Information), and bestbuy.com (Camera Information)

# Authentication
What is the preferred way of using the API? 

# Error Codes
What errors and status codes can a user expect?
200- the API request was successful and data was returned (may be empty data)
404- the API request was not successful

# Rate limit
Is there a limit to the number of requests an user can send?
There is no limit to the number of requests a user can send.
